title: Vampirella (01 - 35) (ongoing) (2010 - 2013) (HD) (- Nem -)
description: The current owners to the rights to Vampirella is Dynamite Entertainment. Her older archive stories are being reprinted, but Dynamite has decided to start their own ongoing series with her. A more modern look Vampirella that has gone away from the pin-up swimsuit outfit version she is famous for. The classic pin-up look is kept traditionally for the cover, so the older collectors can still have their cover girl the way they remember her
